1998;;Thick as Thieves;;American;;Scott Sanders;;Alec Baldwin, Andre Braugher, Rebecca De Mornay;;crime drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thick_as_Thieves_(1998_film);;The film follows an escalating vendetta between professional Chicago thief Mackin (Alec Baldwin) and rising Detroit hood Pointy Williams (Michael Jai White) after an attempted double cross.